259
00:29:17,790 --> 00:29:20,980
Nothing, I’m just annoyed
with a certain charmer.

260
00:29:23,950 --> 00:29:28,290
Does that mean you don’t
wanna go to the movies anymore?

261
00:29:29,310 --> 00:29:32,680
