You promised to take me there after exams.

262
00:29:36,450 --> 00:29:40,470
Then smile.
I want my boyfriend to be happy.

263
00:29:49,670 --> 00:29:51,090
Have you ever ridden a big bike?

264
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,780
What about a big bike’s pillion?

265
00:29:57,210 --> 00:30:00,290
Then today’s your chance.

266
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,220
Really?

267
00:30:27,070 --> 00:30:28,140
Hop on.

268
00:30:45,120 --> 00:30:46,320
Hold properly.

269
00:30:47,270 --> 00:30:53,780
If you touch something you shouldn’t,
I won’t guarantee your safety tonight.

270
00:30:58,650 --> 00:31:00,570
Is there anything you can’t do?

271
00:31:02,030 --> 00:31:03,460
Enviable, right?

272
00:31:05,860 --> 00:31:07,150
Why did you hit me?

273
00:31:07,730 --> 00:31:10,920
What I’m saying is you’re enviable.

274
00:31:15,540 --> 00:31:18,220
Because you have such
a capable boyfriend like me.

275
00:31:23,900 --> 00:31:25,100
Hold tight.

276
00:32:21,810 --> 00:32:25,860
