but still predictable, right?

278
00:32:30,010 --> 00:32:31,780
- Did you enjoy it?
- Yeah.

279
00:32:32,530 --> 00:32:33,630
Are you hungry?

280
00:32:33,810 --> 00:32:36,200
Oh, I’m starving.

281
00:32:36,670 --> 00:32:38,080
What do you wanna eat?

282
00:32:45,550 --> 00:32:46,930
