than when you pursued Ple.

317
00:35:05,930 --> 00:35:08,260
I’ve known about your
relationship with P’ Payu.

318
00:35:08,350 --> 00:35:10,380
I was just waiting for you to tell me.

319
00:35:11,020 --> 00:35:14,900
If you’re afraid to tell me because
P’ Payu’s a man, then you’re crazy.

320
00:35:15,490 --> 00:35:17,590
I’m your friend, not your mom.

321
00:35:18,790 --> 00:35:20,460
Seeing you happy…

322
00:35:22,630 --> 00:35:23,740
That’s enough for me.

323
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:27,110
Sky.

324
00:35:32,270 --> 00:35:33,630
I love you!

325
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:42,710
Before you say you love me,
please look at the man next to you.

326
00:35:46,350 --> 00:35:47,970
I don’t get jealous without reasons.

327
00:35:48,520 --> 00:35:52,880
I know that Sky is Rain’s best friend.

328
00:35:54,720 --> 00:36:01,980
So, can Rain’s best
friend tell me who Ple is?

329
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,340
Hmm?

330
00:36:15,650 --> 00:36:16,860
P’ Payu.

331
00:36:17,350 --> 00:36:21,000
Hey, eat up.
This is the signature dish.

332
00:36:21,020 --> 00:36:23,580
It was very delicious
the last time I ate it.

333
00:36:23,600 --> 00:36:26,220
This restaurant’s top notch.
Eat up. Eat up.

334
00:36:26,870 --> 00:36:28,050
- Delicious?
- Last time?

335
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:31,270
But this is your first time here with me.

336
00:36:33,060 --> 00:36:34,820
- P’ Payu.
- Anoth... Another branch.

337
00:36:34,850 --> 00:36:37,940
Sky! This bread’s good.
Eat it with this dish.

338
00:36:38,030 --> 00:36:39,490
It goes with another dish though.

339
00:36:40,790 --> 00:36:42,350
It goes with that dish too.

340
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:07,860
Please believe me, I don’t have
feelings for Ple anymore.

341
00:37:10,120 --> 00:37:16,350
But didn’t you pursue me to
show Ple that I was a bad guy?

342
00:37:18,110 --> 00:37:20,560
Who… Who says you’re bad?

343
00:37:20,970 --> 00:37:22,000
No one!

344
00:37:22,690 --> 00:37:25,180
You’re apparently nice.

345
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:28,190
Handsome.

346
00:37:28,550 --> 00:37:30,470
Super cool.

347
00:37:30,970 --> 00:37:33,780
And you’re the department’s god
worshipped by juniors.

348
00:37:37,130 --> 00:37:38,570
Believe your boyfriend.

349
00:37:38,970 --> 00:37:40,270
Please.

350
00:37:40,350 --> 00:37:44,920
Pretty, pretty, pretty, pretty please.

351
00:37:45,960 --> 00:37:52,200
Gosh, my friend’s become
silly after he’s got a boyfriend.

352
00:37:54,910 --> 00:37:55,980
Nosy.

353
00:37:57,700 --> 00:37:59,690
What? Hmm?

354
00:38:01,020 --> 00:38:03,950
P’ Payu, eat up.
I’ll feed you.

355
00:38:04,510 --> 00:38:06,510
Do you like it?
It’s your favorite.

356
00:38:06,530 --> 00:38:08,300
- Feed me.
- Sure.

357
00:38:16,640 --> 00:38:18,430
Are you serious, Stop?

358
00:38:19,310 --> 00:38:21,600
You really got an invitation to the race?

359
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:24,610
Why would I lie to you?

360
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:29,650
My dad’s familiar with the
organizer, the influential Mr. Pakin.

361
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:33,180
I can bring you with me.

362
00:38:35,860 --> 00:38:40,410
